    <item>
      <title>日本小泉纯一郎参加领导竞选并表示将举行选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/japan-s-koizumi-enters-leadership-race-says-would-hold-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本前环境大臣小泉进次郎正式宣布参加执政党即将举行的领导人竞选，并表示如果当选将举行大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/japan-s-koizumi-enters-leadership-race-says-would-hold-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 03:56:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国首次以分裂国家罪名判处台湾人监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/china-jails-taiwan-activist-for-nine-years-on-separatism-charge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国以“分裂国家”罪名判处一名台湾政治活动人士九年有期徒刑，这一罕见判决促使台湾警告民众穿越海峡的危险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/china-jails-taiwan-activist-for-nine-years-on-separatism-charge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 02:25:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工会主席抨击美国钢铁公司首席执行官，称公司交易存在缺陷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/nippon-us-steel-deal-union-head-calls-it-flawed-assails-us-steel-ceo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国钢铁工人联合会主席表示，新日本制铁公司需要重新制定与美国钢铁公司的交易，以赢得工会的支持，并建议这家美国公司的董事会考虑更换首席执行官，而美国总统乔·拜登正准备阻止这笔交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/nippon-us-steel-deal-union-head-calls-it-flawed-assails-us-steel-ceo</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 01:10:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯称美国将在未来几天提出加沙方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/israel-hamas-war-us-to-present-gaza-proposal-in-coming-days-blinken-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周四表示，美国、卡塔尔和埃及将在未来几天向以色列和哈马斯提出新的停火方案，而拜登政府正在努力寻找结束加沙地带战争的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/israel-hamas-war-us-to-present-gaza-proposal-in-coming-days-blinken-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 23:57:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Kroger-Albertsons 的未来竞争对手证实她对成功“充满信心”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/kroger-albersons-future-rival-testifies-she-is-confident-of-success</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克罗格公司 (Kroger Co.) 和艾伯森公司 (Albertsons Cos.) 必须出售近 600 家门店才能完成合并，新公司的领导人证实，新公司将拥有中型公司的灵活性，并得到美国最大杂货分销商的购买力支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/kroger-albersons-future-rival-testifies-she-is-confident-of-success</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 22:18:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前国际能源署署长称日本领导人竞选需要核辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/japan-leadership-race-needs-nuclear-debate-ex-iea-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际能源署前署长称，如果日本想要确保长期的经济繁荣和国家安全，那么该国需要在领导人竞选中就核能问题展开更多公开辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/japan-leadership-race-needs-nuclear-debate-ex-iea-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥批准促进债务、股票上市的规则草案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/mexico-approves-draft-rules-to-boost-debt-equity-listings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥财政部副部长加布里埃尔·约里奥周四表示，墨西哥证券监管机构批准了一项旨在促进小公司债务和股票上市的法律草案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/mexico-approves-draft-rules-to-boost-debt-equity-listings</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 18:33:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔最高安全监狱屡遭无人机袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/ecuador-maximum-security-prison-suffers-repeat-drone-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2023 年 9 月，警方在厄瓜多尔一所关押知名囚犯的监狱屋顶引爆了一架携带炸药的无人机，重复了 2023 年 9 月的袭击事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/ecuador-maximum-security-prison-suffers-repeat-drone-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 18:29:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普法官设定选举案审理期限为十月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/trump-defense-spars-with-judge-over-election-timing-in-dc-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[审理唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 2020 年选举干预案的联邦法官为豁免权斗争的下一阶段设定了未来几周的一系列期限，拒绝了前总统律师提出的更为漫长的时间表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/trump-defense-spars-with-judge-over-election-timing-in-dc-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 17:08:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>小泉承诺参选，日本领导人之争愈演愈烈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着最受民众欢迎的候选人之一小泉进次郎的加入，日本执政党总裁选举阵容周五扩大到六人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 02:41:28 GMT</pubDate>
